title: LOL: Last One Laughing Philippines
overview: "LOL" or "Last One Laughing" is a reality show where ten comedians battle it out to make each other laugh. With no smiles allowed, they unleash their best jokes and antics, aiming to make each other crack up for six hours. It's a hilarious battle of wit and self-control, where the last one laughing wins ONE MILLION PESOS!
